8.13	Talwar	Talwar	The talwar (Urdu, Pashto: تلوار, Hindi: तलवार, Marathi: तलवार, Panjabi: ਤਲਵਾਰ, Bangla: তলোয়ার) is a type of curved sword or sabre from India and modern-day Pakistan. The word is also spelled talwaar and tulwar.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/47/The_Damascus_Blade_2.JPG/200px-The_Damascus_Blade_2.JPG
